data.description:
Welcome Home! Escape to the quiet of rural living-3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home. This charming home boasts an amazing layout with brilliant use of space - living room, bonus room, loft & so much more! The ex-lg primary suite features private bath, large closet & tons of sunlight–and the view!
The kitchen is complete w/ample counter space & an adjacent dining area. One of the standout features of this property is the bonus family room downstairs, providing additional space for entertainment, a home office, or a cozy retreat for movie nights. Seller added extra windows when building!

Step outside to discover your own private, wooded yard, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee, hosting barbecues, or simply relishing the quiet of nature.  Less than 1 mile from Rob Wallace park (walkable); 22-minute drive to downtown Concord; easy 30 minute commute to downtown Charlotte – location, location, location! Single car garage w/lots of shelves & an addition parking pad.
